The paper deals with an online optimization problem involving submodular functions, which is a topic commonly studied in the areas of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), game theory (cs.GT), and machine learning (cs.LG). The problem also involves constraints on vector packing, which is a topic studied in information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
